---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Marketing Strategy | Cody Smith" description="SEO, competitive analysis, content direction, and keyword strategy. I direct the marketing. You execute it.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-40 pb-24 px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-1/4 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/services" class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-neutral-500 text-sm hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors duration-300 mb-8 group">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 16l-4-4m0 0l4-4m-4 4h18" />
        </svg>
        All services
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <span class="reveal text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em]">02</span>
        <div class="reveal gradient-divider flex-1"></div>
      </div>
      <h1 class="reveal font-serif text-5xl md:text-7xl text-neutral-100 leading-[1.05] mb-6">
        Marketing Strategy
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal text-neutral-500 italic text-sm tracking-wide mb-10">Decisions and priorities.</p>
      <p class="reveal text-neutral-400 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        You know your marketing could be better, but you don't know where to start. There are too many things competing for attention and no way to tell which ones actually matter. You can't answer "is this working?" with data. I fix that.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What this is / isn't -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 surface-1">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Clarity</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100">What this is.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8">
          <p class="text-amber-400 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-6">This is</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-neutral-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              An SEO roadmap built on real keyword data
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Competitive analysis that names names
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Content briefs your writer can actually use
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Monthly calls to review priorities
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Quarterly reporting with real numbers
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Someone telling you what to stop doing
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8">
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-6">This is not</p>
          <ul class="space-y-4 text-neutral-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
              Social media management
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
              Running your ad campaigns
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
              Writing your blog posts for you
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
              A one-time audit with no follow-through
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
              Vague advice you can't act on
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-neutral-600 mt-0.5">&#10005;</span>
              A retainer for retainer's sake
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How it works -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 dot-grid">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Process</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100">How it works.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-px bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-500/40 via-amber-500/20 to-transparent"></div>

        <div class="space-y-16">
          <div class="reveal relative pl-16 md:pl-20">
            <div class="absolute left-3 md:left-5 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500 bg-neutral-950 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-amber-400 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold">1</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-xl font-medium mb-3">Strategic audit</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
              A full read of your site, your market, and your competitors. Technical SEO, content gaps, keyword opportunities, competitive positioning. Everything gets documented. This is the foundation. Every recommendation that follows traces back to what the audit found.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal relative pl-16 md:pl-20">
            <div class="absolute left-3 md:left-5 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500/60 bg-neutral-950 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-amber-400/60 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold">2</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-xl font-medium mb-3">Prioritized roadmap</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
              The audit findings become a sequenced plan. Not everything matters equally. I tell you what to do first, what can wait, and what you should stop wasting time on. The roadmap has timelines, dependencies, and expected impact.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal relative pl-16 md:pl-20">
            <div class="absolute left-3 md:left-5 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500/40 bg-neutral-950 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-amber-400/40 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold">3</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-xl font-medium mb-3">Monthly direction</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
              Monthly calls to review what's working, what isn't, and what's next. I deliver content briefs, keyword targets, and strategic memos. You or your team execute. I keep the plan on track and adjust when the data says to.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal relative pl-16 md:pl-20">
            <div class="absolute left-3 md:left-5 top-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full border-2 border-amber-500/20 bg-neutral-950 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-amber-400/20 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold">4</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-xl font-medium mb-3">Quarterly measurement</h3>
            <p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">
              Every quarter, a full review: what moved, what didn't, what we're changing. Rankings, traffic, conversions. Real numbers tied to real decisions. No vanity metrics, no spin.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Deliverables -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6 surface-1">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Deliverables</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100">What you get.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 reveal-stagger">
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6" style="--i:0">
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Keyword research</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Real search volume, real difficulty scores, grouped by intent. Not a spreadsheet dump. A prioritized list of opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6" style="--i:1">
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Competitive analysis</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Who's ranking for what you want, what they're doing differently, and where the gaps are that you can exploit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6" style="--i:2">
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Content briefs</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Page-level briefs with target keywords, structure recommendations, and competitive context. Hand these to your writer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6" style="--i:3">
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">SEO roadmap</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Technical fixes, content priorities, and link opportunities, sequenced by impact and effort. Updated quarterly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6" style="--i:4">
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Strategy memos</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">When something needs your attention, like a market shift, a competitor move, or an algorithm update, you get a clear memo with recommended action.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-6" style="--i:5">
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 font-medium mb-2">Quarterly reports</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Rankings, traffic, conversions, and what it means. Executive brief up front, data behind it. Written for decision-makers, not analysts.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tiers -->
  <section class="py-28 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <p class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4">Pricing</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100">Pick your level.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 reveal-stagger">
        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8 flex flex-col" style="--i:0">
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-2">Good</p>
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-2xl font-medium mb-1">Directional</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm mb-6">Audit + roadmap. Know what to do and in what order.</p>
          <ul class="text-neutral-400 text-sm space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Strategic audit
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Keyword research
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Prioritized SEO roadmap
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Monthly check-in call
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-white/10 text-neutral-300 font-medium text-sm rounded-lg hover:border-white/25 hover:text-neutral-100 transition-all duration-300">
            Get started
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8 flex flex-col ring-1 ring-amber-500/30 relative" style="--i:1">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-8 px-3 py-1 bg-amber-500 text-neutral-950 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
            Recommended
          </div>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-2">Better</p>
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-2xl font-medium mb-1">Strategic</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm mb-6">Ongoing strategy with competitive intelligence and content direction.</p>
          <ul class="text-neutral-400 text-sm space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Everything in Directional
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Quarterly competitive analysis
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Content briefs
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Quarterly reporting
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-amber-500 text-neutral-950 font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,158,11,0.25)]">
            Get started
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal glow-card p-8 flex flex-col" style="--i:2">
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-2">Best</p>
          <h3 class="text-neutral-100 text-2xl font-medium mb-1">Embedded</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-500 text-sm mb-6">Strategic partner. I operate like your outsourced marketing director.</p>
          <ul class="text-neutral-400 text-sm space-y-3 mb-8 flex-1">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Everything in Strategic
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Hiring guidance for marketing roles
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Team training included
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-amber-400 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              Strategy memos on demand
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border border-white/10 text-neutral-300 font-medium text-sm rounded-lg hover:border-white/25 hover:text-neutral-100 transition-all duration-300">
            Get started
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative py-32 px-6 surface-1 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[500px] h-[300px] bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="reveal font-serif text-3xl md:text-5xl text-neutral-100 mb-6">Know what you need to do next?</h2>
      <p class="reveal text-neutral-400 text-lg mb-10">If the answer is "not really," that's exactly what this service solves.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="reveal inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-amber-500 text-neutral-950 font-semibold text-sm rounded-lg hover:bg-amber-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(245,158,11,0.25)]">
        Start a conversation
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
